px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-eb556a95-0555-440d-8e67-ef421488db5a\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ebd07d0781b35dda.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"402\", \"originalHeight\" : \"717\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ebd07d0781b35dda.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ebd07d0781b35dda.jpg\" data-width=\"402\" data-height=\"717\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f89bd81c-5491-4409-9df1-486fd3530e44\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b1cfa385-e686-4d29-be3f-47b41032020a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c756ec81-b31d-49e6-a702-2f1aec0b6eef\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-06e1e3a5-3847-437e-8a1b-17b4fcff0909\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-36cbfd80-e0c0-4a4a-8876-7a9c37e2dda4\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4f832fd6-e7de-453e-97b9-807e350c2455\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-10e8e243-4163-49c5-b686-5d1dcf65b52a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e9d2b3d1-3e40-477e-9cf1-fd044b0e90f4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0e968a46-9db5-47e8-b934-74819956c3e4\">대한민국의 봄을 대표하는 풀코스 마라톤인 서울마라톤(구, 동아마라톤)이 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-12e00bad-6af3-420e-83c3-74ae0c442dea\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a7b20c6b-b576-4d61-b402-ea848cd002d1\">한달여 남은 시점이라 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0e5bd55b-b2d2-4463-9d32-a8e1936ce984\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f78a44d5-42de-4040-871d-a83d5bc33a2e\">부상으로 인한 훈련량 부족이 우려되는 상황.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-90112452-99b4-4335-9173-fa2e80d560cd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-443f40d0-d600-42f3-8194-c6144d4cb2b3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3d76a0f0-817f-4476-a512-f884b4e1bc48\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-37242ace-9c11-4b2c-a27f-d0c5a7d2beae\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-55d63620-c8ad-4699-b64a-ba2763552b24\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c099f52a-62d4-4419-ac78-fd2019265f48\">미리 신청해뒀던 동계국제마라톤을 참가할까 말까 몇일을 고민하다가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3ad04ed9-2488-4c95-aa63-fc1c806dac1b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-df576f14-c59d-4979-8555-5e088a3dce73\">부상이 완전 회복된 상태는 아니지만, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-07a6d2d6-7587-4e66-9334-77b499299f4e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f90fc58f-5760-43f3-8393-c8c72320df77\">그렇다고 장거리 훈련을 더 이상 미룰 수도 없는 상황이라</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-77cd06e7-7b5b-4d26-9160-e27826d6819f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4fd3d3a1-30f2-496d-a610-3e8d9ca52db7\">조심조심 부상부위 체크해가면서 살살 뛰기로 하고 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5f64fe62-0326-4e63-82f6-a27effde1a9b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b921a0d5-a894-4adb-9659-6a3afbe15d10\">2월 16일 일요일. 대회에 참가했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-99079595-1dcb-4934-992d-9ac5e13bdb12\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-081415df-5a8d-4108-b0db-60d8e26e23a3\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-370c1b20-a6a2-41a2-9778-756c0753695a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-370c1b20-a6a2-41a2-9778-756c0753695a\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f3878c5372a81efd.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1280\", \"originalHeight\" : \"960\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f3878c5372a81efd.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f3878c5372a81efd.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"375\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ffeb682f-94b9-4f22-8457-a3279bc6f22b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4489c5a3-a71f-4bd3-a933-fa4c6829b2ea\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a1fab1dc-0ee1-4470-b7fe-1eb47614b573\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aeff70b1-2bd7-4c84-90f9-0da40dcfbfc6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-62f52314-3ba3-4af0-914d-6c08148abf43\">대회는 여의도에서 8시 START</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-63f693d2-95f0-4df2-93dd-394b9099ba87\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-599bbbc6-4fc0-4662-b565-fad3564a6c47\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\" >\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-d914530c-8a30-4919-8905-abeb11324983\">\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module='{\"type\":\"v2_video\", \"id\" :\"SE-d914530c-8a30-4919-8905-abeb11324983\", \"data\" : { \"videoType\" : \"player\", \"vid\" : \"7C68F92C1999D60B8BD6A51DD5C4A1FA9859\", \"inkey\" : \"V1259be2e0fc3aacce471225a7425ccead210b07e3f480e89c10879c975732e4b09d7225a7425ccead210\", \"thumbnail\": \"https://phinf.pstatic.net/image.nmv/blog_2025_02_17_3985/IWXHipLaEr_01.jpg\", \"originalWidth\": \"720\", \"originalHeight\": \"1280\", \"width\": \"500\", \"height\": \"888\", \"contentMode\": \"fit\", \"format\": \"normal\", \"mediaMeta\": {\"@ctype\":\"mediaMeta\",\"title\":\"2025 동계국제마라톤\",\"tags\":[],\"description\":null}, \"useServiceData\": \"false\"}}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-68c5d83d-ed7b-44f6-b596-0341c918ab2d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fcd58f68-5d2e-4c23-a6b1-e0b6dbfc0553\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fc249653-926c-4e88-af97-8db45452148f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e3ddc202-f259-4fa9-96cf-cfb7fe601a6f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-81acb620-2f5c-4169-9bfa-b99650e2f750\">첫 반환구간까지 예상외로 잘 달려집니다.  </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-94e24b17-81b0-4fe2-9bb8-a5091cddb550\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-971d70ef-0029-4bd1-ad69-03f730a5d1ca\">&#x27;어라. 몸이 많이 회복된건가?&#x27;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0f710cc1-49cb-476f-afd0-480d3949aad8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-256306c2-e61c-4b71-bca7-0f15907b534b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4f100497-0e70-4701-a645-4186b282cebc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4615a161-2bff-4d40-bc31-bcbf0dc71fe1\">반환점을 돌자마자 맞바람이 ㅜ.ㅠ</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aa5a4673-491b-46d8-b7dc-46c7aaecd71c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ebdf756a-eb84-41c2-b1da-2d729790d61a\">아... 지금까지는 내가 뒷바람을 맞으며 수월하게 달린거였어.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3bddb300-504f-4d87-91ca-fa0a6e7d4c3d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1a1b0d36-3180-4165-8ab7-fadecde26138\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-137bc800-552f-4c4e-bbb4-06990a831aa1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4d26a9b9-ac10-4e63-9895-c3496989c554\">그렇게 하프지점까지는 큰 무리 없이 달렸는데</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0397aced-6bd4-48dd-b276-dbcbbf444d40\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-47b41eb3-0a1b-4f20-a8c5-cf60ccedaaad\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-db3d60